obj_root_law_sections_1:
  sectionId (21434)
  sectionNo (1)
  orderNo 1
  title `Short title, extent and commencement.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_1_content
  footnotes `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21434&sectionno=1&orderno=1&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line `(1) This Act may be called the Armed Forces (Jammu`
  line `and Kashmir) Special Powers Act, 1990.`
  line
  line `(2) It extends to the whole of the State of Jammu and Kashmir*.`
  line
  line `(3) It shall be deemed to have come into force on the 5th day of July, 1990.`
obj_root_law_sections_2:
  sectionId (21435)
  sectionNo (2)
  orderNo 2
  title Definitions.
  content obj_root_law_sections_2_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21435&sectionno=2&orderno=2&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_2_content:
  string
  line `In this Act, unless the context otherwise requires,--`
  line
  line `(a) "armed forces" means the military forces and the air forces operating as land forces and`
  line `includes any other armed forces of the Union so operating;`
  line
  line `(b) "disturbed area" means an area which is for the time being declared by notification under`
  line `section 3 to be a disturbed area;`
  line
  line `(c) all other words and expressions used herein, but not defined and defined in the Air Force Act,`
  line `1950 (45 of 1950), or the Army Act, 1950 (46 of 1950), shall have the meanings respectively`
  line `assigned to them in those Acts.`
obj_root_law_sections_2_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_3:
  sectionId (21436)
  sectionNo (3)
  orderNo 3
  title `Power to declare areas to be disturbed areas.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_3_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21436&sectionno=3&orderno=3&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_3_content:
  string
  line `If, in relation to the State of Jammu and Kashmir*, the Governor of that State or the Central Government, is of opinion that the whole or any part of the State is in such a disturbed and dangerous condition that the use of armed forces in aid of the civil power is necessary to prevent--`
  line
  line `(a) activities involving terrorist acts directed towards overawing the Government as by law established or striking terror in the people or any section of the people or alienating any section of the people or adversely affecting the harmony amongst different sections of the people;`
  line
  line `(b) activities directed towards disclaiming, questioning or disrupting the sovereignty and territorial integrity of India or bringing about cession of a part of the territory of India or secession of a part of the territory of India from the Union or causing insult to the Indian National Flag, the Indian National Anthem and the Constitution of India,`
  line
  line `the Governor of the State or the Central Government, may, by notification in the Official Gazette, declare the whole or any part of the State to be a disturbed area.`
  line
  line `Explanation.--In this section, "terrorist act" has the same meaning as in Explanation to article 248 of the Constitution of India as applicable to the State of Jammu and Kashmir*.`
obj_root_law_sections_3_footnotes:
  string
  line `*. Vide notification No. S.O. 3912(E), dated 30th October, 2019, this Act is made applicable to the Union territory of Jammu`
  line `and Kashmir and the Union territory of Ladakh.`
obj_root_law_sections_4:
  sectionId (21437)
  sectionNo (4)
  orderNo 4
  title `Special powers of the armed forces.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_4_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21437&sectionno=4&orderno=4&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_4_content:
  string
  line `Any commissioned officer, warrant officer, noncommissioned`
  line `officer or any other person of equivalent rank in the armed forces may, in a disturbed`
  line area,—
  line
  line `(a) if he is of opinion that it is necessary so to do for the maintenance of public order, after giving`
  line `such due warning as he may consider necessary, fire upon or otherwise use force, even to the causing`
  line `of death, against any person who is acting in contravention of any law or order for the time being in`
  line `force in the disturbed area prohibiting the assembly of five or more persons or the carrying of`
  line `weapons or of things capable of being used as weapons or of fire-arms, ammunition or explosive`
  line substances;
  line
  line `(b) if he is of opinion that it is necessary so to do, destroy any arms dump, prepared or fortified`
  line `position or shelter from which armed attacks are made or are likely to be made or are attempted to be made, or any structure used as a training camp for armed volunteers or utilised as a hide-out by armed`
  line `gangs or absconders wanted for any offence;`
  line
  line `(c) arrest, without warrant, any person who has committed a cognizable offence or against whom`
  line `a reasonable suspicion exists that he has committed or is about to commit a cognizable offence and`
  line `may use such force as may be necessary to effect the arrest;`
  line
  line `(d) enter and search, without warrant, any premises to make any such arrest as aforesaid or to`
  line `recover any person believed to be wrongfully restrained or confined or any property reasonably`
  line `suspected to be stolen property or any arms, ammunition or explosive substances believed to be`
  line `unlawfully kept in such premises, and may for that purpose use such force as may be necessary, and`
  line `seize any such property, arms, ammunition or explosive substances;`
  line
  line `(e) stop, search and seize any vehicle or vessel reasonably suspected to be carrying any person`
  line `who is a proclaimed offender, or any person who has committed a non-cognizable offence, or against`
  line `whom a reasonable suspicion exists that he has committed or is about to commit a non-cognizable`
  line `offence, or any person who is carrying any arms, ammunition or explosive substance believed to be`
  line `unlawfully held by him, and may, for that purpose, use such force as may be necessary to effect such`
  line `stoppage, search or seizure, as the case may be.`
obj_root_law_sections_4_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_5:
  sectionId (21438)
  sectionNo (5)
  orderNo 5
  title `Power of search to include powers to break open locks, etc.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_5_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21438&sectionno=5&orderno=5&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_5_content:
  string
  line `Every person making a search`
  line `under this Act shall have the power to break open the lock of any door, almirah, safe, box, cupboard,`
  line `drawer, package or other thing, if the key thereof is withheld.`
obj_root_law_sections_5_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_6:
  sectionId (21439)
  sectionNo (6)
  orderNo 6
  title `Arrested persons and seized property to be made over to the police.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_6_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21439&sectionno=6&orderno=6&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_6_content:
  string
  line `Any person arrested and`
  line `taken into custody under this Act and every property, arms, ammunition or explosive substance or any`
  line `vehicle or vessel seized under this Act, shall be made over to the officer-in-charge of the nearest police`
  line `station with the least possible delay, together with a report of the circumstances occasioning the arrest, or`
  line `as the case may be, occasioning the seizure of such property, arms, ammunition or explosive substance or`
  line `any vehicle or vessel, as the case may be.`
obj_root_law_sections_6_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_7:
  sectionId (21440)
  sectionNo (7)
  orderNo 7
  title `Protection of persons acting in good faith under this Act.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_7_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21440&sectionno=7&orderno=7&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_7_content:
  string
  line `No prosecution, suit or other legal`
  line `proceeding shall be instituted, except with the previous sanction of the Central Government, against any`
  line `person in respect of anything done or purported to be done in exercise of the powers conferred by this`
  line Act.
obj_root_law_sections_7_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_sections_8:
  sectionId (21441)
  sectionNo (8)
  orderNo 8
  title `Repeal and saving.`
  content obj_root_law_sections_8_content
  footnotes obj_root_law_sections_8_footnotes
  query abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727&sectionId=21441&sectionno=8&orderno=8&orgactid=AC_CEN_5_23_00016_199021_1517807323727
obj_root_law_sections_8_content:
  string
  line `(1) The Armed Forces (Jammu and Kashmir) Special Powers Ordinance,`
  line `1990 (Ord. 3 of 1990), is hereby repealed.`
  line
  line `(2) Notwithstanding such repeal, anything done or any action taken under the said Ordinance shall be`
  line `deemed to have been done or taken under the corresponding provisions of this Act.`
obj_root_law_sections_8_footnotes:
  string
  line
obj_root_law_translations:
  hi obj_root_law_translations_hi
obj_root_law_translations_hi:
  title `सशस्‍त्र बल (जम्मू-कश्मीर) विशेषशक्‍तियां अधिनियम, 1990`
